version_description: Freja eID has undergone background tweaks resulting in better performance. In addition, we have made fixes and adjustments to the content in the app to make it more user-friendly for you.

Finding an authorised vetting agent to complete Freja eID Plus registration has never been easier - we now show you a list of agents ordered by proximity to your current location.

To increase transparency, we have also improved the visibility of the personal information you are sharing with a service when you are logging in or signing.

Improved registration for people under 18. Other visual and performance improvements.
Like the app? Rate us! Your feedback helps us make Freja eID better.

This update brings improved passport registration for our users in Sweden and Norway, which includes reading data from the passport's NFC chip. We also made some minor tweaks in registration flow for other ID documents to make the onboarding process even smoother for our users.
